<div class='toload lemma'>
	<p><span class='envidentifier'>Lemma 3.3.8</span>
	Under the hypotheses of Proposition <span class='ref' data-tag='propositionuniquemapwhichmakesbasicisthomeomorphism'></span>, $\phi:Y\to X$ is the only map for which $T$ is $\phi$-basic.
	</p>
